responseText: The Zephyr Wind is my own movement, as you seem curious. We represent the spirit of the Vaelune people, subdued for so long. But here on Verra our strength, our sovereignty, is writ across our very faces! It is time that we embrace our gifts, lest we again be subsumed by the tides of the Kaelar.
name: SQ_RVR_NPC_Samias_Miraleth_Sabah_33_Response
